OL,3,C'Cruel and counterproductive':
OL,4,CCharities' plea on rough sleeping
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FHome Secretary James Cleverly is
OL,8,Fcoming under increasing pressure to
OL,9,Freconsider new plans to clamp down on
OL,10,F"nuisance" rough sleepers in England
OL,11,Fand Wales.
OL,13,FA total of 37 charities, including
OL,14,FCrisis, Amnesty UK and the Big Issue,
OL,15,Fhave voiced their concerns in a letter
OL,16,Fto Mr Cleverly warning that measures
OL,17,Fin the Criminal Justice Bill could see
OL,18,Fvulnerable women fined for seeking
OL,19,Fshelter.
