OL,3,C'Cruel and counterproductive':
OL,4,CCharities' plea on rough sleeping
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FCrisis told ITV News the plans are
OL,8,F"cruel and counterproductive" and that
OL,9,Fthe language used in parts of the Bill
OL,10,F- such as the word "nuisance" - is
OL,11,F"demeaning".
OL,13,FThe government is attempting to stave
OL,14,Foff a revolt over the plans with
OL,15,Fplanning to rebel against the
OL,16,Flegislation, fearing it could
OL,17,Fcriminalise homeless people.
