OL,3,C'Cruel and counterproductive':
OL,4,CCharities' plea on rough sleeping
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FMeasures in the Bill would allow
OL,8,Fpolice to move on "nuisance" rough
OL,9,Fsleepers and if they don't comply,
OL,10,Fthey will have powers to fine or
OL,11,Farrest them.
OL,13,FCritics argue the language is so broad
OL,14,Fthat people carrying an "excessive
OL,15,Fsmell" or who merely appear as though
OL,16,Fthey intend to sleep rough could be
OL,17,Ffined up to #2,500.
