OL,3,C'Cruel and counterproductive':
OL,4,CCharities' plea on rough sleeping
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FThe charities' letter praises certain
OL,8,Felements of the Bill designed to end
OL,9,Frough sleeping, but says other parts
OL,10,F"undermine" those commitments.
OL,12,F"It could see women, who are
OL,13,Fdisproportionately likely to suffer
OL,14,Fviolence and sexual abuse on the
OL,15,Fstreets, penalised for seeking shelter
OL,16,Fand safety in well-lit doorways," it
OL,17,Fadds.
