OL,3,C'Cruel and counterproductive':
OL,4,CCharities' plea on rough sleeping
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FJasmine Basran, Head of Policy and
OL,8,FCampaigns at Crisis, told ITV News:
OL,9,F"Elements of the Bill - aside from the
OL,10,Foverall approach - really go into
OL,11,Fpersonal, dehumanising attacks on
OL,12,Fpeople."
OL,14,FThe charity is "incredibly worried"
OL,15,Fabout the measures and is urging the
OL,16,Fhome secretary to "listen" to their
OL,17,Fconcerns and meet with them, said Ms
OL,18,FBasran.
