OL,3,C'Cruel and counterproductive':
OL,4,CCharities' plea on rough sleeping
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FFormer ministers Sir Iain Duncan Smith
OL,8,Fand Damian Green are among 10 Tories
OL,9,Fwho have signed a series of amendments
OL,10,Fto the Bill aimed at countering the
OL,11,Fdrive to criminalise rough sleeping.
OL,13,FMeasures tabled by Tory MP Bob
OL,14,FBlackman would seek to ensure
OL,15,Fministers fulfil their promise to
OL,16,Frepeal the Vagrancy Act 1824, the law
OL,17,Fwhich currently criminalises rough
OL,18,Fsleeping and begging.
