OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FThe government promised to do so when
OL,8,Fit passed the Police, Crime,
OL,9,FSentencing and Courts Act in 2022, but
OL,10,Fonly when it found a suitable
OL,11,Freplacement.
OL,13,FMeasures in the Criminal Justice Bill
OL,14,Faim to provide this replacement but
OL,15,Fare thought to be too widely drawn by
OL,16,Fthe Tory rebels.
OL,18,FA second amendment from Mr Blackman
OL,19,Faims to clarify when the police are
OL,20,Fable to use the new powers.
